title: HiKey 960
overview_main_specification: Powered by Kirin 960, HiKey 960 provides top in class performance around all mobile SoC. It conforms to the Linaro 96boards open development board specification and has reserved a rich standard external I/O extension interface, which can be applied to the external I/O equipment, display and camera in the 96Boards ecosystem.
3GB LPDDR4 SDRAM/ 32GB UFS flash storage/ microSD card slot
40 pin low speed expansion connector: +1.8V, +5V, DC power, GND, 2UART, 2I2C, SPI, I2S, 12*GPIO
60 pin high speed expansion connector: 4L-MIPI DSI, I2C x2, SPI (48M), USB 2.0, 2L+4LMIPI CSI
